title: Falcon 9 launch with Arabsat 7B set for Friday
summary: SpaceX will make another attempt to launch the Arabsat 7B satellite to geostationary transfer orbit (GTO) for Arabsat atop its Falcon 9 rocket. Friday’s attempt is hoping to avoid weather issues that have caused two delays in the previous launch attempts.
